⍝ Solution: sum first 15 digits of each number, extract first 10 digits
⍝ APL handles big integers natively, so we can just sum all numbers
∇ R ← Solve nums;total;s
  total ← +/{⍎⍵}¨nums
  s ← ⍕total
  R ← ⍎10↑s
∇

result ← Solve nums
⎕ ← 'Result: ' , ⍕result
